name: TLSP Jellyfish Shirt
description: These 100% cotton bad boys have jellyfish on em. Colored in 2 (count em 2) shades of blue, along with the band's name, set on your classic black tee. We have them in small, medium and large, perfect for going to a show in...and yeah, you'll pretty much look awesome in them.

name: Jellyfish Button
description: These buttons are a limited time thing, because we don't have many left. Stick it to your hat, stick it to your pants...we don't really care where you stick these lovelies, just show em of proudly. It's got a bright pink jellyfish on it, complete with lyrics from "Ethereal" set against a white background.

name: Precursor EP
description:
These is the first EP from The Last Six Pages, self-recorded at CCC Studios in Ohio. 5 tracks from your favorite post-hardcore band. Unfortunately, being the first recordings, there is no album art...but the discs are handwritten on. =)

"Precursor" Track Listing:

1. Amiable Persona
2. Social Butterfly Collection
3. Lost At Sea
4. Whirlwind
5. A Fear Of Waking Up To Nothing
